{"tid":426723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿古路禍不單行 撞車後畀女友飛","createTime":"2017-10-07T01:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T11:38:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb92186eecab685c4a35fb0b77b5af6ec38c0fc","tid":426723,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"曼城前鋒阿古路上星期喺荷蘭遇到車禍導致肋骨骨裂，可能要養傷四個星期，估唔到嘅係原來佢禍不單行，撞完車兩日就畀女友Karina Tejeda飛埋！<br />\n<br />\n29歲嘅阿古路係睇完哥倫比亞歌手Maluma嘅演唱會之後，搭的士去機場途中架的士失控撞埋燈柱度受傷，喺阿根廷方面就有報道話，同阿古路拍咗拖四年嘅31歲歌手女友Karina Tejeda已經同佢分手。據英國《太陽報》報道，Karina Tejeda同阿古路分手係因為嬲對方喺上次國際賽期返阿根廷嘅時候，同國家隊隊友參加咗有唔少性感model同場嘅party喎，而佢事先並唔知阿古路會去呢個party。<br />\n有報道話阿古路試圖用喺Instagram like Karina嘅性感相等方法去挽救呢段感情，不過Karina話自己都係喺一個阿根廷記者度知道阿古路撞車嘅消息，似乎係想同佢劃清界線。"},{"pid":"acba593b9e13d2508e8844f8429c9a8523aa754b","tid":426723,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/093813_bfe4e116faf6c770508be3deabd8c703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F093813_bfe4e116faf6c770508be3deabd8c703.jpg&h=4aca6bf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"746e775c521b21ac012f8846a901163f0ccc83d3","tid":426723,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/093813_bfe4e116faf6c770508be3deabd8c703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F093813_bfe4e116faf6c770508be3deabd8c703.jpg&h=4aca6bf4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n個樣咁都有女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1167f685321de0d35999aaf79d8f94252c7d20f","tid":426723,"uid":1289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3915f8528581fd4dacb8b27c890176706da16a2f","tid":426723,"uid":5170